snippet.title: LEGO Star Wars™: The Skywalker Saga - DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
New legendary characters have landed in the galaxy! Who will you play as first?
 
Get LEGO Star Wars™: The Skywalker Saga today! https://go.wbgames.com/LSWG_Purchase
 
DLC Character Packs Currently Available:
- The Mandalorian: Season 1 Character Pack
- The Mandalorian: Season 2 Character Pack
- Solo: A Star Wars Story Character Pack
- Classic Character Pack
- Trooper Character Pack
- Rogue One: A Star Wars Story Character Pack
- The Bad Batch Character Pack

The galaxy is yours with LEGO Star Wars™: The Skywalker Saga! Play through all nine saga films in a brand-new video game unlike any other. With over 300 playable characters, over 100 vehicles, and 23 planets to explore, the galaxy has never been more fun!
 
Join us on our Social Channels!

Instagram: https://go.wbgames.com/LSWG-Instagram
